com_google_testparameterinjector.build_file_content:
java_library(
    name = "testparameterinjector",
    testonly = True,
    srcs = glob(["src/main/**/*.java"]),
    deps = [
      "@org_snakeyaml//:snakeyaml",
      "@//third_party:auto_value",
      "@//third_party:guava",
      "@//third_party:junit4",
      "@//third_party/protobuf:protobuf_java",
    ],
    visibility = ["//visibility:public"],
)
com_google_testparameterinjector.name: com_google_testparameterinjector
